summary: It explodes through your body to your head with a blinding darkness. It made you dizzy. It made you reel. You felt like needles...
caption:
It explodes through your body to your head with a blinding darkness. It made you dizzy. It made you reel. You felt like needles had been dipped into a deadly poison and were being jammed into your flesh. 

You clench your hands into fists so hard, you draw droplets of blood from your own palms. All the sudden a piercing scream erupts from within you and Thanos widens his eyes in fear as he brings himself to his knees at the sight of your horrific wrath.

album: David Bowie (aka Space Oddity) [2015 Remastered Version]
caption:
Okay but imagine in avengers endgame Tony’s like accepting his death as space oddity is playing in the background, and as Tony’s closing his eyes for the last time the music fades and the light from the nearest star is eclipsed by some nearby planet, fading the screen to black as the last part of the song plays 

Though I’m past one hundred thousand miles
I’m feeling very still
And I think my spaceship knows which way to go
Tell my wife I love her very much she knows
Ground Control to Major Tom
Your circuit’s dead, there’s something wrong
Can you hear me, Major Tom?
Can you hear me, Major Tom?
Can you hear me, Major Tom?
Can you “Here am I floating ‘round my tin can
Far above the moon
Planet Earth is blue
And there’s nothing I can do”

And then the screen suddenly starts to brighten again, and Captain Carol motherfuckin Danvers comes out of nowhere to Tony’s rescue and all star by smash mouth plays as she kicks in the spaceship door

body:
Avengers 4 Spoiler?

Okay so idk where the original post is but someone was saying how Steve looking at Peggy’s photo is because she got turned to dust and when they mention losing friends and family that he was thinking of her. Idk why it bothered me but that is not the case. Peggy has already died in Civil War and that’s why they had the whole funeral. That was when Steve found out that Sharon was her niece and that they were related.
